definitions.definition: A local government area in the Greater Western Sydney region of New South Wales , Australia ; in full, the City of Parramatta .
A suburb in western Sydney , in the City of Parramatta, New South Wales .
A river in Sydney , New South Wales , flowing through the suburb and into Sydney Harbour ; in full, the Parramatta River .
An electoral division in Sydney , New South Wales , Australia .
An electoral district in Sydney , New South Wales , Australia .
